# Illustration for the problem of qwtplot3d with recent Qt5 versions

## Building

    export QMAKE=qmake-qt5

    sh build-svn.sh

    sh build-sintegrial.sh


## Problem

When closing the the example application, it receives a SIGSEGV.

Arch (Qt 5.14.2-1)


